name: Rockabilly Nautical Hair Clip
description:
Miss Rockabilly creates 1950s pin up inspired hair accessories, jewelry and more.

This is one of my latest nautical inspired hair bows. Feel like a trip to the beach on a quiet boat drifting off into the sunset? A summery design perfect to compliment Navy outifts and pin up sailor dresses.

Created with soft navy and ivory striped grosgrain ribbon and attached to an alligator clip for easy hair application. White resin anchor buoy button attached.

Soft and delicate. Destined to make you feel like a 1950s pin up girl.

Approximately 3.8" L x 2.5" H (90mm L x 60mm H)

Thanks for looking!

name: Gingham Hot Pink Shoe Clips
description:
Miss Rockabilly creates 1950s pin up inspired hair accessories, jewelry and more.

One of the many shoe clips available from Miss Rockabilly.

Inspired by gingham and tartan, this is a set of 2 gingham bow shoe clips. Clip them over your shoes to create a whole new look. Great for changing up shoes you have worn before. Would look great with hot pink, black or white shoes

Measuring approximately 65mm L x 25mm H (2.5” L x 1.5” H). 

The bows fastened to silver shoe clips and just open and close over the top of your shoe to secure in place.

These can be also turned into hair clips. Just ask!

Thank you for stopping by.

For the love of everything Pin Up! Bringing back 40s and 50s fashion for women. Miss Rockabilly is all about feeling sexy and looking classy and at the same time wearing something totally unique!

name: Swallow Ring
description:
Miss Rockabilly creates 1950s pin up inspired hair accessories, jewelry and more.

Inspired by nautical and whimsical themes, this blue resin swallow ring is one of it's kind. 

The swallows have been moulded, poured, sanded and coated by myself. They are very unique. No two rings are ever the same from colour mixing. This little swallow is a light blue hue with slight white marbling throughout. 

Attached to a brushed silver adjustable ring to suit any finger! Great quality brushed silver.

Swallows can be custom made in any colour so contact me with an idea! They are all made from scratch. Please allow an extra 3 days for custom colours due to pouring, setting, sanding and coating.

45mm L x 35mm H (2" L x 1.5" H)

Thank you for stopping by.

Any shipping discrepancies are refunded via Paypal if they work out cheaper than quoted to post.

For the love of everything Pin Up! Bringing back 40s and 50s fashion for women. Miss Rockabilly is all about feeling sexy and looking classy and at the same time wearing something totally unique!

name: Pin Up Bottle Cap Necklaces
description:
Miss Rockabilly creates 1950s pin up inspired hair accessories, jewelry and more.

Pin Up Girl Bottle Cap Necklaces. The newest additions from Miss Rockabilly. Affordable and oh so sweet!

This listing is for ONE necklace of your choice

*Choose your own Pin Up Girl Image
*Choose your own Necklace colour. Most are available.

Necklace Colours: White, Black, Ruby Red, Pink, Navy, Blue, Light Blue, Olive Green, Lime Green, Brown, Purple, Yellow and Orange.

A matching swarovski crystal will also be added to the adjustable chain to suit! Necklace consists of Organza Ribbon and leather.

Bottle cap images are protected to prevent wear

Necklace Length - 410mm L (16")

Sits perfectly around your neck and can be adjusted to suit.
